'''铀钒镇'''（{{lang-en|Uravan}}，“[[铀|铀]]”与“[[钒|钒]]”对应的英文拼写的[[混成词|混成词]]<ref>{{cite book|last=Dawson|first=John Frank|title=Place names in Colorado: why 700 communities were so named, 150 of Spanish or Indian origin|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015051116740;view=1up;seq=56|publisher=The J. Frank Dawson Publishing Co.|location=Denver, CO|page=50}}</ref>）是美国[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]西部[[蒙特羅斯縣|蒙特羅斯縣]]为了采集铀矿而建起的小镇，现已废弃。<ref name=GNIS>{{cite gnis|id= 203153 |name=Uravan|accessdate=2011-02-17}}</ref>[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间，[[曼哈顿计划|曼哈顿计划]]从该镇购买了730吨的铀矿。<ref>{{cite book |last=Hewlett |first=Richard G. |last2=Anderson |first2=Oscar E. |title=The New World, 1939–1946 |location=University Park|publisher=Pennsylvania State University Press |year=1962 |url=https://www.governmentattic.org/5docs/TheNewWorld1939-1946.pdf|access-date=26 March 2013|isbn=0-520-07186-7|oclc=637004643}}</ref>

